Hello! I'm Jon, a responsible and trustworthy individual who believes in maintaining high standards in everything I do. I own a restoration company named Prime Restoration, where attention to detail and reliability are key to my success.

I love exploring new places and have had some amazing travel experiences. One of my favorite trips was to Madrid, Spain, where I loved the vibrant culture and delicious food.

When I'm not working or traveling, I enjoy a variety of hobbies. I love trying new foods and have a club with friends where we explore different cuisines from around the world. I'm also passionate about baseball, camping, and off-roading. Most importantly, I cherish spending time with my little family.

With years of driving experience under my belt, I ensure my vehicles are always well-maintained and clean. I own a 2015 Lexus GX, a 2013 Hyundai Sonata Hybrid, a 2021 Ford F150, and a 2018 Toyota Rav4, all of which are kept in excellent condition for a smooth and enjoyable ride.

I'm looking forward to providing you with a great car rental experience!

bio.openEndedText: My name is Louis Boakye. I am a father of a beautiful baby boy and married for 4 years. I am an advertising major, currently in schools. I enjoy a lot of active activities such as basketball, exercising and soccer. I love watching movies with good story lines. I hope that the service I am providing will help your stay in Utah more comfortable.

I've loved cars for as long as I can remember and always dreamed of owning a fleet of cars. Thanks to you, I'm actually doing it! I drive every car in my fleet to make sure it passes what I would want to rent personally. Every car to me is special because of the memories they create and adventures they enable. Even a commute to work can be more enjoyable with a fun car. I hope you enjoy my cars as much as I do!
